      <trans-unit id="7268960255192550849" datatype="html">
        <source> Rafael is a frontend developer with several years of experience building modern, fast, and enjoyable interfaces. He works daily with HTML5, CSS3, TypeScript, and frameworks like Vue and Angular. He values clean, well-structured code and the balance between performance and design. </source>
